content:
Once your managed package is certified through our security review, you can make it available to your customers by uploading it to AppExchange. To distribute a CRM Analytics managed package:

Submit your package for a security review.
Before a package can be listed on AppExchange, it must meet established standards.

When your package is ready, click Upload, then fill in the required information:
Add version specifics, including name and version number.
Choose the release type—Managed - Beta or Managed - Released—and an appropriate version number.
Add a description for your AppExchange listing.

Click Upload.
Use the License Management Application to manage user-based licenses. You can request the application through your partner community site.

Note: Deployment requires Salesforce admin permissions.
title: Deploying CRM Analytics Assets on AppExchange
